{"tid":2340142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解密文件:  日本政府在六四當天就反對制裁中國","createTime":"2020-12-25T08:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T08:52:19.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"822764844004b828c6379824492cd383f0250bab","tid":2340142,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"2020/12/23 18:02<br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕根據日本政府今天公開的外交文件，中國1989年發生天安門事件後，日本政府當天就決定對中國採取和睦的應對方針，反對與西方各國共同制裁中國。<br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）報導，日本政府外務省今天公開1987年到1990年的26冊外交文件，總頁數約1萬600頁。<br />\n<br />\n這次公開的外交文件中，包括與天安門事件相關的紀錄，也明載日本政府在事發當天就決定對中國採取和睦的應對方針。<br />\n.........<br />\n日本政府認為，如果給予跟西方國家共同譴責中國這樣的印象，將迫使中國走向孤立，「從長期整體局勢的角度來看，並非上策」，明確記載日本反對與西方各國共同制裁中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3390092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390092&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQKVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=37a54d02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390092&h=6884d3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3390092</a>"},{"pid":"b0ed6801da22dd284e3c900e5fb388870356a1c2","tid":2340142,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:07:09.000Z","msg":"日本就係俾當年政府攪彎哂,&nbsp;失落30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e950f3a923fbff4259f432a11ba9fae0ebef48d4","tid":2340142,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0e6a96d4688b4de06fc9d586f55d967e34d7aa5","tid":2340142,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e950f3a923fbff4259f432a11ba9fae0ebef48d4","tid":2340142,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"呢班人累死日本<img src